{"tid":1488784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆眼女義士有機會連陽光都見唔到，你仲要J差婆？","createTime":"2019-08-19T16:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T01:37:10.000Z","uid":143945,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"960316a6d6280309ce899b8a70e09c5e1ab3509c","tid":1488784,"uid":143945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:50:56.000Z","msg":"我知入夜可能出面推po開po嘅係$0.3<br />\n<br />\n但以正視聽，我地唔可以比女義士知道佢為我地奉上一雙眼、一個樣 <br />\n換黎大家比個差婆distract哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你諗下狗屋入面班狗笑緊我地成村人係到J隻比狗屌到爛嘅狗乸。<br />\n你地係J緊人地玩到厭唔玩嘅玩具。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試想一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你比狗拉左，如果你訓緊係醫院，你屋企人睇住連登同你講點解你咁傻要為班人付出。<br />\n你係醫院果陣佢地仲J緊差婆啊。 <br />\n你會有咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nJ完過黎幫手推<br />\n絲打們，幫手推上去提下佢地"},{"pid":"40bb1b2e7dcd784a90bf04fc0bc469e1a0782a47","tid":1488784,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:51:53.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"073bc4dac8a349c9b1af68d0a498d29c9ee0bfb6","tid":1488784,"uid":143945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:52:23.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4